{"tid":137868,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 毒果再次幫香港揚名海外!!!","createTime":"2017-02-28T06:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T07:24:23.000Z","uid":84759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4607844d6842d30229c2259c4e09e12adce1f49","tid":137868,"uid":84759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"Emma Stone拿下Oscar影后，接受傳媒訪問。<br />\n<br />\n中途，有香港傳媒問了一個問題，結果，引來同場記者發笑、Emma變面、網民更鬧該香港記者無禮、不尊重、問題簡直是攻擊和侮辱相關演員。<br />\n<br />\n該問題是：<br />\n&quot;My name is XX, I'm from Hong Kong XX (Newspaper). Do you feel like owing Emma Watson a drink or dinner to thank her for turning down the role?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n你好，我是XX，來自香港的XX報紙，當日Emma Watson（哈利波特中的妙麗）推辭角色，你有否覺得自己欠她一餐飯或一杯飲品？<br />\n<br />\n套用該報用語，應該是：<br />\n你果陣執妙麗二攤，有無諗過要同人哋講聲多謝？<br />\n<br />\n結果，外地網民出來鬧，有些說：「香港啲人太無禮貌！」「香港記者咁唔專業架？」「點解會俾個記者問埋啲咁嘅問題？」亦有些自稱是香港人出來幫理不幫親：「呢份報紙最叻無風起浪！」醜死人。<br />\n<br />\n有些問題，香港演員忍你，不代表你問得對。言論自由，大前題是至少要懂得尊重人，否則，你發的聲音，同動物怪叫無分別。<br />\n<br />\n是那份報紙，無必要講，我們要的，不是指責或罵戰，但作為讀者觀眾，我們是時候慎選讀物，別再看這些影響自己質素、影響香港整體水平的報導。<br />\n<br />\n我們要做好自己。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-atl3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/17021911_1833483316892236_5242242867315266818_n.jpg?oh=4b301a37d02dd8d3a6eebb78cf2f18a0&amp;oe=59430B5D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-atl3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F17021911_1833483316892236_5242242867315266818_n.jpg%3Foh%3D4b301a37d02dd8d3a6eebb78cf2f18a0%26oe%3D59430B5D&h=57985ddb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇片 6:03開始<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NsfT6D9YQN8?t=6m3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNsfT6D9YQN8%3Ft%3D6m3s&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=dc89fbb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NsfT6D9YQN8?t=6m3s</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/245V7dx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F245V7dx.jpg&h=305226c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170227/56361467\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170227%2F56361467&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL1eK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=3909e89a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170227%2F56361467&h=8dc1f76c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170227/56361467</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港再次出名!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451f0c74d72c7fcce64bca2bf994d3fc2d84d386","tid":137868,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:06:51.000Z","msg":"妙麗根本唔啱做Mia，啱做belle<br />\n<br />\n問果個有冇睇過戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629b76455cc669224b97f04b6aa9f637a9bf12b8","tid":137868,"uid":16383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:10:40.000Z","msg":"好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fe8080636cd4decb9cb5c7370858f7fc68f850","tid":137868,"uid":24308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1787d1e5b682894150996303ad5dab2f2c09ffcb","tid":137868,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fc2ef1d51dd78102dd1b6f225f4f42c4c32d50","tid":137868,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:24:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>毒果收皮<br />\n<br />\n黎智英仆街死</strong></span></span>"}]}